title: Week 17 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, RB Redemption Tour - Fantasy Football Podcast for 1/3
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Championship Week! What does it mean for future dynasty outlooks? Plus, injury updates, and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for January 3rd, 2022.
  
 (04:00) - Monday Punday
 (06:15) - NFL News 
 (16:15) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (16:20) - QB Studs

 (43:50) - TE Studs
 (45:05) - Fantasy Duds
 (45:10) - QB Duds
 (47:25) - RB Duds
